---
description: Prefer existing workspace and ContractSpec surfaces before creating new code or dependencies
alwaysApply: true
globs:
  - '**/*'
---
Use the ContractSpec Adoption Engine before inventing new local code:

- Resolve reuse in this order: workspace-local implementation -> ContractSpec OSS catalog -> family-specific ecosystem fallback -> new implementation.
- Run `contractspec connect adoption sync --json` to refresh the local catalog when needed.
- Run `contractspec connect adoption resolve --family <family> --stdin --json` when the correct reusable surface is unclear.
- Treat `rewrite` results as actionable: reuse the recommended candidate instead of creating a duplicate.
- Treat `require_review` as blocking for new dependencies or new implementations.
